description: Returns a MemberAccounts object that lists the member accounts in the administrator's Amazon Web Services organization. Either an Firewall Manager administrator or the organization's management account can make this request.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: If you have more member account IDs than the number that you specified for MaxResults in the request, the response includes a NextToken value. To list more IDs, submit another ListMemberAccounts request, and specify the NextToken value from the response in the NextToken value in the next request.
